евозможно удостовериться, что мука не представляет угрозы для хранения и дальнейшего использования.</p><p>Сотрудники Россельхознадзора приняли решение не допускать муку на внутренний рынок. Ведомство подчеркивает, что подобные меры необходимы для предотвращения распространения вредителей, которые могут нанести ущерб запасам зерна и другим сельскохозяйственным продуктам.</p><p>В последнее время контроль за импортом продуктов питания в Петербурге заметно ужесточился. Власти уделяют особое внимание качеству и безопасности товаров, поступающих из-за рубежа. Это связано с ростом числа случаев выявления нарушений при ввозе различных партий продукции.</p><p>Пока неизвестно, будет ли возвращена задержанная партия в страну-отправитель или утилизирована на территории России. Представители контролирующих органов отмечают, что подобные ситуации возникают регулярно, и напоминают импортерам о необходимости строго соблюдать все требования к оформлению документов и проведению лабораторных испытаний.</p></div>	https://spbdnevnik.ru/uploads/block/image/1134897/__medium_495928afd7e74bb84e85784f2f69801d.jpg.jpg	0	f	f	f
1388	1121	NEIGHBORHOOD Collaborates with Graffiti Artist CHITO on Apparel Collection	neighborhood-collaborates-with-graffiti-artist-chito-on-apparel-collection	published	2025-12-12 08:46:41+00	3	17	\N	SummaryNEIGHBORHOOD and graffiti artist CHITO released an apparel collectionThe pieces feature distressed SAVAGE denim and CHITO’s Finesse Pup motifThe collection is now available at NEIGHBORHOOD s...	NEIGHBORHOOD Collaborates with Graffiti Artist CHITO on Apparel Collection	<p><img width="620" src="https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fimage%2F2025%2F12%2F12%2Fneighborhood-chito-collaboration-collection-release-info-000.jpg?w=800&cbr=1&q=90&fit=max" /></p><div>SummaryNEIGHBORHOOD and graffiti artist CHITO released an apparel collectionThe pieces feature distressed SAVAGE denim and CHITO’s Finesse Pup motifThe collection is now available at NEIGHBORHOOD stores and select retailersNEIGHBORHOOD has collaborated with street graffiti artist CHITO on a new apparel collection. This release channels CHITO's bold, free-spirited graffiti energy onto NEIGHBORHOOD's signature vintage-treated garments.The collection lineup offers a wide range of apparel, including T-shirts, sweatshirts, denim pants, and denim jackets. These items are based on NEIGHBORHOOD's "SAVAGE" series and feature realistic aging effects with distressing. Each piece incorporates CHITO's signature character, the Finesse Pup. The standout piece is undoubtedly the denim jacket, which transforms the Finesse Pup motif into a statement piece through cowhide patches, distressing, and rework stitching covering the entire back panel. Beyond the clothing line, a three-dimensional replica of the Finesse Pup will also be released as an incense chamber.With prices ranging from $298 USD to $1,778 USD, the NEIGHBORHOOD x CHITO collection is available now via NEIGHBORHOOD's directly managed stores, online store, and authorized retailers nationwide. Check out the full range above.</div><p><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2025/12/neighborhood-chito-collaboration-collection-release-info" title="NEIGHBORHOOD Collaborates with Graffiti Artist CHITO on Apparel Collection" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here to view full gallery at Hypebeast</a></p>	\N	2025-12-14 11:07:04.468+00	2025-12-13 13:07:06.279+00	published	2025-12-14 11:07:04.483+00	2025-12-14 11:07:04.483+00	t	\N	<p><img width="620" src="https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fimage%2F2025%2F12%2F12%2Fneighborhood-chito-collaboration-collection-release-info-000.jpg?w=800&cbr=1&q=90&fit=max" /></p><p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li>NEIGHBORHOOD and graffiti artist CHITO released an apparel collection</li><li>The pieces feature distressed SAVAGE denim and CHITO’s Finesse Pup motif</li><li>The collection is now available at NEIGHBORHOOD stores and select retailers</li></ul><p><a href="https://hypebeast.com/tags/neighborhood">NEIGHBORHOOD</a> has collaborated with street graffiti artist <a href="https://hypebeast.com/tags/chito">CHITO</a> on a new apparel collection. This release channels CHITO's bold, free-spirited graffiti energy onto NEIGHBORHOOD's signature vintage-treated garments.</p><p>The collection lineup offers a wide range of apparel, including T-shirts, sweatshirts, denim pants, and denim jackets. These items are based on NEIGHBORHOOD's "SAVAGE" series and feature realistic aging effects with distressing. Each piece incorporates CHITO's signature character, the Finesse Pup. The standout piece is undoubtedly the denim jacket, which transforms the Finesse Pup motif into a statement piece through cowhide patches, distressing, and rework stitching covering the entire back panel. Beyond the clothing line, a three-dimensional replica of the Finesse Pup will also be released as an incense chamber.</p><p>With prices ranging from $298 USD to $1,778 USD, the NEIGHBORHOOD x CHITO collection is available now via NEIGHBORHOOD's directly managed stores, <a href="https://www.neighborhood.jp/">online store</a>, and authorized retailers nationwide. Check out the full range above.</p><p><a href="https://hypebeast.com/2025/12/neighborhood-chito-collaboration-collection-release-info" title="NEIGHBORHOOD Collaborates with Graffiti Artist CHITO on Apparel Collection" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Click here to view full gallery at Hypebeast</a></p><p>    <a href="http://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/jump?iu=/1015938/Hypebeast_RSS_300x250_Rectangle&sz=300x250&c=66266" target="_blank" rel="noopener">        <img src="http://pubads.g.doubleclick.net/gampad/ad?iu=/1015938/Hypebeast_RSS_300x250_Rectangle&sz=300x250&c=66266" />    </a></p>	https://image-cdn.hypb.st/https%3A%2F%2Fhypebeast.com%2Fimage%2F2025%2F12%2F12%2Fneighborhood-chito-collaboration-collection-release-info-000.jpg?w=800&cbr=1&q=90&fit=max	1	f	f	f
