на Сайте).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n	<style>\n.user-agreement {\n    font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n    color: #222;\n    max-width: 900px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    padding: 20px;\n}\n.agreement-block h1 {\n    font-size: 26px;\n    margin-bottom: 20px;\n    color: #111;\n}\n.agreement-content h2 {\n    font-size: 20px;\n    margin-top: 28px;\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    color: #111;\n}\n.agreement-content p {\n    margin-bottom: 12px;\n    font-size: 15px;\n}\n.section-divider {\n    margin: 40px 0;\n    border: none;\n    border-top: 2px solid #e3e3e3;\n}\n</style>\n\n<div class="user-agreement">\n  <div class="agreement-block">\n    <h1>Contact</h1>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class="agreement-content">\n\n    <h2>How to Contact Us</h2>\n    <p>\n      If you have any questions, suggestions, or feedback regarding the operation of our Website,\n      you can reach out to us using the contact information below.\n    </p>\n\n    <h2>Email</h2>\n    <p>\n      The primary and preferred method of communication is email:\n      <br><strong>contact@SiteName.com</strong>\n    </p>\n\n    <p>\n      We do our best to respond as quickly as possible. Response time may vary depending on workload,\n      time zone, and the complexity of the request.\n    </p>\n\n    <hr class="section-divider">\n\n    <h2>Additional Contact Methods</h2>\n    <p>\n      In the future, we may add a contact form or additional communication channels.\n      Any updates will be reflected on this page.\n    </p>\n\n    <hr class="section-divider">\n\n    <h2>Please Note</h2>\n    <p>When contacting us, keep in mind:</p>\n\n    <ul>\n      <li>we do not accept legally binding notifications via social media;</li>\n      <li>for personal data inquiries, please refer to our Privacy Policy;</li>\n      <li>for advertising-related questions, refer to the Advertising Policy (if available on the Website).</li>\n    </ul>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n	2025-12-13 11:10:24.807+00	2025-